summary.span: 表示停駐容器內公開停駐屬性的控制項。

span.span: Represents controls that expose their dock properties within a docking container.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 停駐容器是可讓子系的排列方式項目，以水平和垂直，相對於停駐的容器和容器內其他項目界限的控制項。A docking container is a control that allows the arrangement of child elements, both horizontally and vertically, relative to the boundaries of the docking container and other elements within the container. 根據其目前疊置順序; 彼此相對於停駐控制項大於其 z 軸順序放置，進一步說明置順序的指定停駐容器的邊緣。Controls are docked relative to each other based on their current z-order; the higher their z-order placement, the further they are placed from the specified edge of the docking container. 請參閱[Control Pattern Mapping for UI Automation Clients](~/docs/framework/ui-automation/control-pattern-mapping-for-ui-automation-clients.md)如需範例，可以實作此控制項模式的控制項。See [Control Pattern Mapping for UI Automation Clients](~/docs/framework/ui-automation/control-pattern-mapping-for-ui-automation-clients.md) for examples of controls that can implement this control pattern. 不支援任何停駐容器的屬性或任何屬性可能會停駐至停駐容器內目前控制項相鄰的控制項。 does not support any properties of the docking container or any properties of controls that might be docked adjacent to the current control within the docking container.
